      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "USP_ProjectChangeClone",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to clone a project change record from an existing one, identified by "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "@originalId",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", into a new record for a specified fiscal year ("
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "@fy",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "). It also handles associated project change details, filtering out obsolete entries based on agency codes and budget group IDs that do not match the current fiscal year. The procedure returns the new project change ID and a list of obsolete agency codes and budget group IDs."
        }
      ]
    },
